ount: 38 for multiple frontend nodes.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend->recommendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Calls to RecommendationService/ListRecommendations saw average latency decreases, possible due to fast failures or network connection issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal average duration: ~118341ms; Anomaly duration: ~10050ms, smaller by over 10x, with a pattern of likely fast failures.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"ProductCatalogService/GetProduct exhibited mild latency anomaly with a slight increase during the timeframe.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Normal duration: ~10037ms; Anomaly average: ~11148ms.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Context deadline exceeded repeatedly for AdService calls, suggesting downstream AdService may have been the root.\"\n      \"evidence\": \"Status combination shows 552 occurrences of 'context deadline exceeded' from frontend to adservice during the anomaly.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
